  <!--
    Date        : 2026-06-01
    Rule ID     : 110045
    Rule Desc   : FortiGate config CHANGED recovery — re-tag after compliance 120023 overrides
    Original    : 120023 level=8 (GDPR Art 5, compliance overlay, no fortigate_wuh group)
